name: ENDELLION - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character ENDELLION, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. ENDELLION may be small in size but is big in appetite. She loves to eat all the burnt NFTs from all the different platforms and is reknowned for her burnt NFT barbecues which are really big events in the URCORNYVERSE. She loves disco music and if she isn’t eating she is dancing.
